  "body": "**Version info**: teku/v0.11.4-dev-0182e8da/osx-x86_64/oracle-java-12\r\n\r\nMy Teku instance lost connection to all Peers after a bunch of the following warnings:\r\n\r\n`2020-06-10 07:14:28.853+10:00 | nioEventLoopGroup-3-16 | WARN  | DefaultChannelPipeline | An exceptionCaught() event was fired, and it reached at the tail of the pipeline. It usually means the last handler in the pipeline did not handle the exception.\r\nio.netty.handler.timeout.ReadTimeoutException: null`\r\n\r\nTeku continued syncing but it did not reconnect to its Peers.\r\n\r\n",
